"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_open\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>)</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_quit\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_open\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>(<replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable>)</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_quit\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2490
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_continue;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_continue;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2492 index.docbook:3204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> toolbar button and lets "
"the playback continue if it is paused."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Continua</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i "
"permet que la reproducció continuï si està en pausa."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2500
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_pause;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_pause;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2506
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_copy;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_copy;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2508
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the content of the current selection to the clipboard. If the "
"selection is empty, this command does nothing and the content of the "
"clipboard remains unchanged. Only the content of the currently selected "
"tracks is copied to the clipboard!"
msgstr ""
"Copia el contingut de la selecció actual al porta-retalls. Si la selecció "
"està buida, aquesta ordre no farà res i el contingut del porta-retalls no "
"canviarà. Només es copiarà al porta-retalls el contingut de les pistes "
"seleccionades."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2519 index.docbook:2714
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2525
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_crop;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_crop;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2527
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_crop;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_crop;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Crops the signal to the current selection by deleting everything that is "
"after and before the current selection. Affects all tracks. If nothing is "
"selected this command does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Escapça el senyal a la selecció actual suprimint tot el que hi hagi abans i "
"després de la selecció actual. Afectarà totes les pistes. Si no se "
"selecciona res, aquesta ordre no farà res."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2537
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_cut;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_cut;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2539
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_cut;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_cut;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the content of the current selection to the clipboard and removes it "
"from the signal. If the selection is empty, this command does nothing and "
"the content of the clipboard remains unchanged. Only the content of the "
"currently selected tracks is copied to the clipboard, but the selected range "
"is deleted from all tracks."
msgstr ""
"Copia el contingut de la selecció actual al porta-retalls i l'elimina del "
"senyal. Si la selecció està buida, aquesta ordre no farà res i el contingut "
"del porta-retalls no canviarà. Només es copiarà al porta-retalls el "
"contingut de les pistes seleccionades, però l'interval seleccionat serà "
"eliminat de totes les pistes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2551
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;d"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;d"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2554
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;</"
"command>( <replaceable>milliseconds</replaceable>, <replaceable>command</"
"replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;</"
"command>( <replaceable>mil·lisegons</replaceable>, <replaceable>ordre</"
"replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes a <replaceable>command</replaceable> after a given delay. Please "
"note that the command is executed asynchronously after the given time has "
"elapsed. Multiple commands can be queued, where the delays are relative to "
"the last queued command. This command is intended to be used for queuing "
"commands when taking screenshots for documentation purposes."
msgstr ""
"Executa una <replaceable>ordre</replaceable> després d'un retard indicat. "
"Tingueu en compte que l'ordre s'executarà de forma asíncrona després d'haver "
"transcorregut un temps determinat. Es poden establir múltiples ordres, on "
"els retards seran relatius a l'última ordre a la cua. Aquesta ordre està "
"pensada per a utilitzar ordres a la cua quan es prenen captures de pantalla "
"amb finalitats de documentació."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2569 index.docbook:2609 index.docbook:2654 index.docbook:2692
#: index.docbook:2710 index.docbook:2732 index.docbook:2755 index.docbook:2771
#: index.docbook:2799 index.docbook:2814 index.docbook:2864 index.docbook:3054
#: index.docbook:3088 index.docbook:3137 index.docbook:3163 index.docbook:3243
#: index.docbook:3267 index.docbook:3289 index.docbook:3459 index.docbook:3492
#: index.docbook:3562 index.docbook:3576 index.docbook:3591 index.docbook:3986
#: index.docbook:4023 index.docbook:4060 index.docbook:4094 index.docbook:4118
#: index.docbook:4152 index.docbook:4203 index.docbook:4231 index.docbook:4256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Parameters</title>"
msgstr "<title>Paràmetres</title>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>milliseconds</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>mil·lisegons</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2571
#, no-c-format
msgid "number of whole milliseconds to wait before executing the command"
msgstr "nombre de mil·lisegons a esperar abans d'executar l'ordre"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2572 index.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>command</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>ordre</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2573
#, no-c-format
msgid "a command, including parameters to be executed after the given delay"
msgstr ""
"una ordre, inclosos els paràmetres a executar després de la demora indicada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_sync\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_sync;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_resize\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_window_click\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_sendkey\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_window_close\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_screenshot\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_sync\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_sync;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_resize\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_window_click\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_sendkey\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_window_close\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;</"
"command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_window_screenshot\"><command>&no-"
"i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2589
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_delete;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_delete;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2591
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_delete;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_delete;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes the currently selected range of samples. If the selection is empty, "
"this command does nothing. Affects all tracks."
msgstr ""
"Suprimeix l'interval seleccionat de les mostres. Si la selecció està buida, "
"aquesta ordre no farà res. Afectarà totes les pistes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2601
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_delete_track;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_delete_track;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_delete_track;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_delete_track;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes a track, identified by its index (starting from zero). If no track "
"with the given index exists, this command exits with an error."
msgstr ""
"Suprimeix una pista, identificada pel seu índex (començant pel zero). Si no "
"hi ha cap pista amb l'índex indicat, aquesta ordre sortirà amb un error."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2610 index.docbook:2733 index.docbook:2772 index.docbook:2800
#: index.docbook:3563 index.docbook:3577 index.docbook:3592
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>index</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>índex</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2610
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the track to delete, starting with 0"
msgstr "índex de la pista a suprimir, començant pel 0"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2615
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_dump_metadata;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_dump_metadata;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_dump_metadata;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_dump_metadata;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prints a list of all meta data entries to the console, for diagnostic "
"purposes. (Only available when &kwave; has been compiled with the option "
"<literal>WITH_DEBUG</literal> switched on)."
msgstr ""
"Imprimeix a la consola una llista de totes les entrades de metadades, amb "
"finalitats de diagnòstic. (Només estarà disponible quan s'hagi compilat el "
"&kwave; amb l'opció <literal>WITH_DEBUG</literal> activada)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2627
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;e"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;e"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2630
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_expandtolabel;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_expandtolabel;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_expandtolabel;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_expandtolabel;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Expands the current selection to the labels left and right from the current "
"selection borders. If the border of selection already is on a label, it "
"stays unchanged. If there is no label left or right of the current "
"selection, it will be expanded to the start or end of the file."
msgstr ""
"Expandeix la selecció actual a les etiquetes esquerra i dreta a partir de "
"les vores de la selecció actual. Si la vora de la selecció ja es troba en "
"una etiqueta, es mantindrà sense canvis. Si no hi ha cap etiqueta a "
"l'esquerra o dreta de la selecció actual, s'expandirà fins al començament o "
"al final del fitxer."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2644
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;f"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;f"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2647
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_fileinfo;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_fileinfo;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_fileinfo;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_fileinfo;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set a file info entry to a new value."
msgstr "Estableix una entrada d'informació del fitxer a un valor nou."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>keyword</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>paraula_clau</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "keyword of the entry"
msgstr "paraula clau de l'entrada"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2656
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>value</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>valor</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2656
#, no-c-format
msgid "value of the entry"
msgstr "valor de l'entrada"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2661
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_forward;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_forward;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_forward;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_forward;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips forward by 1/10 of the visible "
"range. If the playback is not running, this does the same as the command "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Endavant</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. Si la "
"reproducció s'està executant, saltarà endavant per 1/10 de l'interval "
"visible. Si la reproducció no s'està executant, aquesta farà el mateix que "
"l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_right\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_rewind"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_right\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_rewind"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2681
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;g"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;g"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2684
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_goto;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_goto;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_goto;</command>(<replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_goto;</command>(<replaceable>posició</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the cursor to the given position and makes it visible in current view. "
"After this the selection has zero length."
msgstr ""
"Estableix el cursor a la posició indicada i la fa visible a la vista actual. "
"Després d'això, la selecció tindrà una longitud de zero."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2693 index.docbook:2711 index.docbook:2756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>pos</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>posició</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2693
#, no-c-format
msgid "position in samples where to go to"
msgstr "posició en mostres on anar"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2698
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;i"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;i"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2701
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_insert_at;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_insert_at;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_insert_at;</"
"command>(<replaceable>pos</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_insert_at;</"
"command>(<replaceable>posició</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the content of the clipboard at the given position, like the command "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>(). If the clipboard is currently "
"empty, this function does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Insereix el contingut del porta-retalls a la posició indicada, com ara "
"l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>(). Si el porta-retalls està "
"buit, aquesta funció no farà res."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid "position in samples where to insert"
msgstr "posició en mostres on inserir"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_insert_track;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_insert_track;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_insert_track;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_insert_track;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a new track at the given index, using the current length and sample "
"rate settings of the signal. If the index is higher than or equal to the "
"current number of tracks, it will be appended as the last track, same as by "
"the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_add_track;</command>(). The index of all "
"existing tracks at and after the given index will be incremented by one."
msgstr ""
"Insereix una pista nova a l'índex indicat, utilitzant les opcions de la "
"longitud i freqüència de mostreig del senyal. Si l'índex és superior o igual "
"que el nombre actual de pistes, s'annexarà com a última pista, igual que per "
"a l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_add_track;</command>(). L'índex de totes les "
"pistes existents en i després de l'índex indicat s'incrementarà en un."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the track to insert, starting with 0"
msgstr "índex de la pista a inserir, començant pel 0"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2737
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_add_track;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_add_track;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2743
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;l"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;l"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2746
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_label_add;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_label_add;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_add;</"
"command>(<replaceable>pos</replaceable>[,<replaceable>text</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_add;</"
"command>(<replaceable>posició</replaceable>[,<replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a new label at a given position. If the given position already contains "
"a label, then this command does nothing. The label can be given an optional "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Afegeix una etiqueta nova en una posició indicada. Si la posició indicada ja "
"conté una etiqueta, llavors aquesta ordre no farà res. L'etiqueta pot "
"indicar una descripció opcional."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2756
#, no-c-format
msgid "position in samples where to insert the label"
msgstr "posició en mostres on inserir l'etiqueta"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2757 index.docbook:3055
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>text</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>text</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2757
#, no-c-format
msgid "some descriptive text (optional)"
msgstr "algun text descriptiu (opcional)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2762
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_label_delete;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_label_delete;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_delete;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_delete;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes a label, identified by its index (starting from zero), or all labels "
"when using the special value -1 as index. If no label with the given index "
"exists, this command does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Suprimeix una etiqueta, identificada pel seu índex (començant pel zero), o "
"totes les etiquetes quan s'utilitza el valor especial -1 com a índex. Si no "
"hi ha cap etiqueta amb l'índex indicat, aquesta ordre no farà res."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"index of the label to delete, starting with 0 or -1 to delete all labels"
msgstr ""
"índex de l'etiqueta a suprimir, començant pel 0 o -1 per a suprimir totes "
"les etiquetes"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2778
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2780 index.docbook:4379 index.docbook:4419 index.docbook:4564
#: index.docbook:4923 index.docbook:5231 index.docbook:5424 index.docbook:5460
#: index.docbook:5550 index.docbook:5643 index.docbook:5706 index.docbook:5750
#: index.docbook:5868 index.docbook:5943 index.docbook:6061 index.docbook:6154
#: index.docbook:6460 index.docbook:6685 index.docbook:6799 index.docbook:6810
#: index.docbook:6948 index.docbook:7002
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the label editing dialog"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla del diàleg «Edició de l'etiqueta»"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog window in which the user can edit the position and the "
"description of a label, which is identified by its index (starting from "
"zero). If no label with the given index exists, this command does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Obre un diàleg on l'usuari podrà editar la posició i la descripció d'una "
"etiqueta, el que s'identificarà amb el seu índex (començant pel zero). Si no "
"hi ha cap etiqueta amb l'índex indicat, aquesta ordre no farà res."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2800
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the label to edit, starting with 0"
msgstr "índex de l'etiqueta a editar, començant pel 0"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2805
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;</"
"command>(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;</"
"command>(<replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a &kwave; script file and processes the commands in it. Uses the "
"context of the currently opened file or the current main window if no file "
"is loaded."
msgstr ""
"Obre un fitxer de script del &kwave; i en processa les ordres. Utilitza el "
"context del fitxer actualment obert o la finestra principal si no hi ha cap "
"fitxer carregat."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2815 index.docbook:3138 index.docbook:3164 index.docbook:3460
#: index.docbook:3493 index.docbook:4234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>filename</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>nom_de_fitxer</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2816
#, no-c-format
msgid "name of the kwave script file including path and extension"
msgstr "nom del fitxer de script del &kwave;, inclòs el camí i l'extensió"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2821
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_loop;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_loop;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2823
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_loop;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_loop;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Loop</guibutton> toolbar button. Starts the "
"playback (if it is not already running) and lets it play in a loop."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Repeteix</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. "
"Inicia la reproducció (si encara no s'està executant) i permet reproduir en "
"un bucle."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2832
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2838
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;m"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;m"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2841
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_menu;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_menu;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</command> "
"(<replaceable>command</replaceable>, <replaceable>path</replaceable>, "
"[<replaceable>hotkey</replaceable>], [<replaceable>id</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</command> (<replaceable>ordre</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>camí</replaceable>, [<replaceable>drecera</"
"replaceable>], [<replaceable>id</replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a very powerful command, which is used to add a new entry to the "
"menu or to modify an existing entry. It determines which <emphasis>command</"
"emphasis> is executed when the menu entry is activated, which "
"<emphasis>icon</emphasis> is shown in the menu and which <emphasis>hotkey</"
"emphasis> is used. Each menu entry can be <emphasis>disabled</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>hidden</emphasis>, can be assigned a unique <emphasis>id</"
"emphasis> and can also join a <emphasis>menu group</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Es tracta d'una ordre molt potent, la qual s'utilitza per a afegir una "
"entrada nova al menú o per a modificar una entrada existent. Determina quina "
"<emphasis>ordre</emphasis> s'executarà quan s'activi l'entrada del menú, "
"quina <emphasis>icona</emphasis> es mostrarà al menú i quina "
"<emphasis>drecera de teclat</emphasis> s'utilitzarà. Cada entrada de menú es "
"pot <emphasis>inhabilitar</emphasis> o <emphasis>ocultar</emphasis>, se li "
"pot assignar un <emphasis>id</emphasis> únic i també pot unir-se a un "
"<emphasis>grup del menú</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid "You normally do not need this command within a &kwave; script!"
msgstr "Normalment no necessitareu aquesta ordre dins d'un script del &kwave;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A text command (including parameters) or a command list that will be "
"executed when the menu entry gets activated. If a menu entry does not have a "
"corresponding command (for example if it is a sub menu and not menu entry), "
"you should use the special command <command>ignore</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Una ordre de text (inclosos els paràmetres) o una llista d'ordres que "
"s'executarà quan s'activi l'entrada del menú. Si una entrada de menú no té "
"una ordre corresponent (&pex;, si es tracta d'un submenú i no d'una entrada "
"del menú), haureu d'utilitzar l'ordre especial <command>ignore</command>()."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2876
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>path</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>camí</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The path within the menu, using a <quote><token>/</token></quote> as "
"separator. The last part of the path can be a <emphasis>sub command</"
"emphasis> which modifies some property of the menu entry (see <link linkend="
"\"menu_sub_commands\">below</link>). The last portion of the path (that is "
"not a sub command) produces a menu entry, the parts before produce the main "
"menu entry or sub menus that lead to it. Main menu entries or sub menus are "
"automatically created when a menu entry is created, you do not need them "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"El camí dins del menú, utilitzant un caràcter de «<token>/</token>» com a "
"separador. L'última part del camí podrà ser una <emphasis>subordre</"
"emphasis>, la qual modificarà algunes propietats de l'entrada del menú "
"(vegeu a <link linkend=\"menu_sub_commands\">continuació</link>). L'última "
"porció del camí (no és una subordre) produeix una entrada del menú, les "
"parts abans de produir l'entrada del menú principal o els submenús que ens "
"porten a ella. Les entrades del menú principal o submenús es crearan "
"automàticament quan es creï una entrada del menú, no cal crear-les "
"manualment."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>hotkey</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>drecera</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A bitmask that consists of a combination of predefined <emphasis>keys</"
"emphasis> and <emphasis>modifiers</emphasis>, concatenated with a "
"<quote><token>+</token></quote>. The <emphasis>key</emphasis> can be either "
"a digit, an upper case letter, a function key (<quote>F1</quote> ... "
"<quote>F12</quote>) or any other key name understood by the Qt class "
"<quote><literal>QKeySequence</literal></quote>, including key names for "
"predefined actions (like for example <quote><literal>::Copy</literal></"
"quote>). Typical <emphasis>modifiers</emphasis> are <quote><literal>SHIFT</"
"literal></quote>, <quote><literal>ALT</literal></quote> and "
"<quote><literal>CTRL</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Una màscara de bits que consisteix en una combinació de <emphasis>tecles</"
"emphasis> i <emphasis>modificadors</emphasis> predefinits, concatenats amb "
"un caràcter de «<token>+</token>». La <emphasis>tecla</emphasis> pot ser un "
"dígit, una lletra majúscula, una tecla de funció («F1» fins a la «F12») o "
"qualsevol altre nom de tecla entès per la classe «<literal>QKeySequence</"
"literal>» de les Qt, inclosos els noms de tecla per a accions predefinides "
"(com per exemple «<literal>::Copy</literal>»). Els <emphasis>modificadors</"
"emphasis> típics són «<literal>SHIFT</literal>», «<literal>ALT</literal>» i "
"«<literal>CTRL</literal>»."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2909
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>id</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>id</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unique id that can be internally used to identify this menu entry or "
"menu / sub menu. Only uppercase letters, digits and <quote><literal>_</"
"literal></quote> should be used and it should start with "
"<quote><literal>ID_</literal></quote>. It is in your own responsibility to "
"make sure that the same id is not used twice."
msgstr ""
"Un id únic que es pot utilitzar internament per a identificar aquesta "
"entrada del menú o menú/submenú. Només s'han d'utilitzar lletres majúscules, "
"dígits i el caràcter «<literal>_</literal>», i hauria de començar amb "
"«<literal>ID_</literal>». És responsabilitat vostra assegurar-vos que el "
"mateix id no s'utilitza dues vegades."

# skip-rule: punctuation-colon-no
#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sub Commands"
msgstr "Subordres:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2922
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#checkable</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#checkable</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Makes the menu entry <emphasis>checkable</emphasis>, so that it can be "
"switched on or off."
msgstr ""
"Fa que l'entrada de menú <emphasis>es pugui marcar</emphasis>, de manera que "
"es podrà activar o desactivar."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2928
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#disabled</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#disabled</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2929
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Disables</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>Inhabilita</emphasis> el menú, l'entrada del menú o submenú."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#enabled</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#enabled</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Enables</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>Habilita</emphasis> el menú, l'entrada del menú o submenú."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#exclusive</command>(<replaceable>group</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#exclusive</command>(<replaceable>grup</replaceable>):"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the menu entry to an <emphasis>exclusive</emphasis> "
"<emphasis><replaceable>group</replaceable></emphasis> (one of many "
"selection). The group that is given as parameter should not be used for any "
"other purpose. Only one entry within that group can be selected at a time."
msgstr ""
"Afegeix l'entrada del menú a un <emphasis><replaceable>grup</replaceable></"
"emphasis> <emphasis>exclusiu</emphasis> (una de moltes seleccions). El grup "
"que s'indica com a paràmetre no s'haurà d'utilitzar per a cap altra "
"finalitat. Només es podrà seleccionar una entrada alhora dins d'aquest grup."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2947
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#group</command>(<replaceable>list</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#group</command>(<replaceable>llista</replaceable>):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the menu, sub menu or menu entry to one or more a <emphasis>groups</"
"emphasis>, so that the application can enable/disable a bunch of menu "
"entries without need to know all their unique ids. Multiple groups can be "
"passed as a list with a <quote><literal>,</literal></quote> as separator. "
"Group names have to start with a <quote><literal>@</literal></quote>. The "
"following groups are predefined:"
msgstr ""
"Afegeix el menú, l'entrada del menú o submenú a un o més <emphasis>grups</"
"emphasis>, de manera que l'aplicació pot habilitar/inhabilitar un munt "
"d'entrades del menú sense necessitat de conèixer tots els seus id únics. Es "
"poden passar múltiples grups com una llista amb un caràcter de «<literal>,</"
"literal>» com a separador. Els noms de grup hauran de començar amb un "
"caràcter de «<literal>@</literal>». Hi ha predefinits els grups següents:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2959
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@CLIPBOARD</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@CLIPBOARD</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only enabled when the clipboard is not empty."
msgstr "Només estarà habilitat quan el porta-retalls no estigui buit."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@LABELS</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@LABELS</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only enabled when the current signal contains at least one label."
msgstr ""
"Només estarà habilitat quan el senyal actual contingui almenys una etiqueta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2976
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@NOT_CLOSED</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@NOT_CLOSED</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when the current signal is not closed (the signal might be empty or "
"zero length)."
msgstr ""
"Habilitat quan el senyal actual no estigui tancat (el senyal podrà estar "
"buit o amb longitud zero)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2985
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SELECTION</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SELECTION</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when the selection is not empty (more than one sample is selected)."
msgstr ""
"Habilitat quan la selecció no estigui buida (hi haurà més d'una mostra "
"seleccionada)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2994
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SIGNAL</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SIGNAL</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when there is some signal loaded and it is not empty or zero length."
msgstr ""
"Habilitat quan hi hagi algun senyal carregat i no estigui buit o amb "
"longitud zero."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3005
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#hidden</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#hidden</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3006
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Hides</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>Oculta</emphasis> el menú, l'entrada del menú o submenú."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3009
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#icon</command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#icon</command>(<replaceable>nom</replaceable>):"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assigns an <emphasis>icon</emphasis> to the menu entry. The icon "
"<emphasis><replaceable>name</replaceable></emphasis> should correspond to an "
"icon file (without path and file extension) that is installed on the system "
"or with &kwave;."
msgstr ""
"Assigna una <emphasis>icona</emphasis> a l'entrada del menú. El "
"<emphasis><replaceable>nom</replaceable></emphasis> de la icona haurà de "
"correspondre a un fitxer d'icona (sense camí ni extensió de fitxer) "
"instal·lat al sistema o amb el &kwave;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>#listmenu</command>(<replaceable>id</replaceable>,"
"<replaceable>command</replaceable>):"
msgstr ""
"<command>#listmenu</command>(<replaceable>id</replaceable>,"
"<replaceable>ordre</replaceable>):"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a placeholder for a list of menu entries into a sub menu. The unique "
"<emphasis><replaceable>id</replaceable></emphasis> specified in this sub "
"command is used to add/remove or clear the list of menu entries. The "
"<emphasis><replaceable>command</replaceable></emphasis> parameter has to "
"contain <quote><literal>%1</literal></quote> as parameter, which will be "
"replaced with the text of the menu entry when it is activated. This sub "
"command is internally used for the list of recent files, list of tracks and "
"window list."
msgstr ""
"Insereix un marcador de posició per a una llista d'entrades del menú dins "
"d'un submenú. L'<emphasis><replaceable>id</replaceable></emphasis> únic "
"especificat en aquesta subordre s'utilitzarà per a afegir/treure o esborrar "
"la llista d'entrades del menú. El paràmetre <emphasis><replaceable>ordre</"
"replaceable></emphasis> haurà de contenir «<literal>%1</literal>» com a "
"paràmetre, el qual serà substituït pel text de l'entrada del menú quan sigui "
"activada. Aquesta subordre s'utilitza internament per a la llista de fitxers "
"recents, llista de pistes i llista de finestres."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3033
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#separator</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#separator</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserts a separator into a sub menu."
msgstr "Insereix un separador dins d'un submenú."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3044
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;</command>(<replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;</command>(<replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a message box with some <emphasis><replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"emphasis> and the two buttons <guibutton>OK</guibutton> (returns without "
"error code) and <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> (returns and error code). You "
"can use this command to give the user a possibility to abort a running "
"script."
msgstr ""
"Mostra un quadre de missatge amb algun <emphasis><replaceable>text</"
"replaceable></emphasis> i dos botons <guibutton>D'acord</guibutton> (retorna "
"sense codi d'error) i <guibutton>Cancel·la</guibutton> (retorna amb un codi "
"d'error). Podeu utilitzar aquesta ordre per a donar a l'usuari la "
"possibilitat d'interrompre un script en execució."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A message that will be shown in the message box, should contain a question "
"that can be answered with <guibutton>OK</guibutton> or <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Un missatge que es mostrarà al quadre de missatge, haurà de contenir una "
"pregunta que es podrà respondre amb <guibutton>D'acord</guibutton> o "
"<guibutton>Cancel·la</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3066
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;n"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;n"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3069
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;</"
"command>( <replaceable>samples</replaceable>, <replaceable>rate</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>bits</replaceable>, <replaceable>tracks</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;</"
"command>( <replaceable>mostres</replaceable>, <replaceable>taxa</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>bits</replaceable>, <replaceable>pistes</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new signal, with a given length in <emphasis><replaceable>samples</"
"replaceable></emphasis>, a <emphasis><replaceable>rate</replaceable></"
"emphasis> in samples per second (floating point number), a number of "
"<emphasis><replaceable>bits</replaceable></emphasis> per sample and number "
"of <emphasis><replaceable>tracks</replaceable></emphasis>. You can calculate "
"the length in samples by multiplying the desired length in seconds with the "
"sample rate."
msgstr ""
"Crea un senyal nou, amb una longitud determinada en "
"<emphasis><replaceable>mostres</replaceable></emphasis>, una "
"<emphasis><replaceable>taxa</replaceable></emphasis> en mostres per segon "
"(nombre en coma flotant), un nombre de <emphasis><replaceable>bits</"
"replaceable></emphasis> per mostra i nombre de "
"<emphasis><replaceable>pistes</replaceable></emphasis>. Podeu calcular la "
"longitud en les mostres, multiplicant la longitud desitjada en segons amb la "
"freqüència de mostreig."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3089
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>samples</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>mostres</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length of the signal in samples."
msgstr "Longitud del senyal en mostres."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>rate</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>taxa</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Sample rate in samples per second.</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Freqüència de mostreig en mostres per segon.</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>bits</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>bits</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Number of bits per sample, must not be zero, should be a number from 8...32."
msgstr ""
"El nombre de bits per mostra, no haurà de ser zero, haurà de ser un número "
"entre 8 i 32."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>tracks</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>pistes</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of tracks."
msgstr "Nombre de pistes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3102
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_next;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_next;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3104
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips forward to the next label. If the "
"playback is not running, this does the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Següent</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. Si "
"s'està executant la reproducció, saltarà endavant cap a la propera etiqueta. "
"Si la reproducció no s'està executant, aquesta farà el mateix que l'ordre: "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_prev\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_prev\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;o"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;o"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3125
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_open;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_open;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>([<replaceable>filename</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>([<replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a file, which can be either a sound file or a &kwave; script. If no "
"file name is passed, then a dialog window will be opened that allows to "
"select an existing file. Depending on the &GUI; mode the file will be opened "
"in the context of a new sub-window (MDI and tab) or in a new main window "
"(SDI, if there was already something loaded)."
msgstr ""
"Obre un fitxer, el qual pot ser un fitxer de so o un script del &kwave;. Si "
"no es passa cap nom de fitxer, s'obrirà un diàleg que permeti seleccionar un "
"fitxer existent. Segons el mode de la &IGU;, el fitxer s'obrirà en el "
"context d'una subfinestra nova (MDI i Pestanyes) o en una finestra principal "
"nova (SDI, si ja hi havia quelcom carregat)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3139
#, no-c-format
msgid "name of a file including path and extension"
msgstr "nom d'un fitxer, inclòs el camí i l'extensió"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3143 index.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3149
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;</"
"command>(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;</"
"command>(<replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Practically the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>(), "
"but intended to be used internally for the list of recently opened files in "
"the menu <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenu>Open Recent</guimenu> "
"</menuchoice>. In this command the parameter <replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable> is not optional."
msgstr ""
"Fa pràcticament el mateix que l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>(), però es pretén utilitzar internament per a la llista de fitxers "
"oberts recentment al menú <menuchoice> <guimenu>Fitxer</"
"guimenu><guimenu>Obre un de recent</guimenu> </menuchoice>. En aquesta "
"ordre, el paràmetre <replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable> no és opcional."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3165
#, no-c-format
msgid "entry of the list of recently opened files"
msgstr "entrada de la llista dels fitxers oberts recentment"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3175
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;p"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;p"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3178
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_paste;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_paste;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3180
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replaces the current selection with the content of the clipboard. If the "
"clipboard is empty, this command does nothing. The sample rate of the "
"inserted data is adjusted to match the sample rate of the current signal if "
"necessary. Only enabled tracks are affected, disabled tracks remain "
"unchanged. Please be aware that this might produce a time shift between "
"enabled and disabled tracks! If the number of tracks of the clipboard data "
"differs from the number of enabled tracks, then the data is mixed to be "
"spread equally over all selected tracks."
msgstr ""
"Substitueix la selecció actual amb el contingut del porta-retalls. Si el "
"porta-retalls està buit, aquesta ordre no farà res. Si és necessari, la "
"freqüència de mostreig de les dades introduïdes s'ajustarà perquè "
"coincideixi amb la freqüència de mostreig del senyal actual. Només afectarà "
"les pistes habilitades, les pistes inhabilitades no es modificaran. Tingueu "
"en compte que això podria produir un desplaçament en el temps entre les "
"pistes habilitades i les inhabilitades. Si el nombre de pistes de les dades "
"al porta-retalls difereix del nombre de pistes habilitades, llavors les "
"dades es barrejaran per a ser distribuïdes equitativament entre totes les "
"pistes seleccionades."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3202
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_pause;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_pause;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Pause</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback pause if it is currently running, or continue if it is currently "
"paused."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Pausa</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i permet "
"fer una pausa en la reproducció si s'està executant, o continuar si es troba "
"en pausa."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3219
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback start if it is currently paused."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Inicia</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i permet "
"iniciar la reproducció si es troba en pausa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3230
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(<replaceable>name</"
"replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(<replaceable>nom</"
"replaceable>, [<replaceable>paràmetre</replaceable> «...»])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes a plugin, with an optional list of parameters. If no parameter list "
"is given, then the setup function of the plugin will be called, using the "
"parameters of the previous invocation or default parameters as input "
"(normally shows a setup dialog, depending on the plugin). Please refer to "
"the chapter about <link linkend=\"plugins\">plugins</link> for a description "
"of the various plugins."
msgstr ""
"Executa un connector, amb una llista opcional de paràmetres. Si no s'indica "
"cap llista de paràmetres, llavors es cridarà la funció de configuració del "
"connector, utilitzant els paràmetres de la crida anterior o amb els "
"paràmetres predeterminats com a entrada (normalment es mostrarà un diàleg de "
"configuració, depenent del connector). Consulteu el capítol sobre els <link "
"linkend=\"plugins\">connectors</link> per a obtenir una descripció dels "
"diferents connectors."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3244 index.docbook:3268 index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>name</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>nom</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3245 index.docbook:3269 index.docbook:3291
#, no-c-format
msgid "the (internal) name of a &kwave; plugin"
msgstr "el nom (intern) d'un connector del &kwave;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3246 index.docbook:3270 index.docbook:3292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>parameter</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>paràmetre</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3247 index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "a list of parameters understood by the plugin (optional)"
msgstr "una llista dels paràmetres entesos pel connector (opcional)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_execute\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_plugin_execute;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_setup"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_execute\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_plugin_execute;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_setup"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3258
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;</"
"command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</"
"replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;</"
"command>(<replaceable>nom</replaceable>, [<replaceable>paràmetre</"
"replaceable> «...»])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(), but "
"without calling the setup function of the plugin if no parameters were "
"passed."
msgstr ""
"Similar a l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(), però sense "
"cridar la funció de configuració del connector si no s'ha passat cap "
"paràmetre."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid "a list of parameters understood by the plugin"
msgstr "una llista dels paràmetres entesos pel connector"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3276
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</"
"command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</"
"replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</"
"command>(<replaceable>nom</replaceable>, [<replaceable>paràmetre</"
"replaceable> «...»])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calls the <emphasis>setup</emphasis> function of a plugin, with an optional "
"list of parameters. If no parameter list is given, the parameters of the "
"previous invocation or default parameters will be used as input. This "
"normally shows a setup dialog, depending on the plugin. Please refer to the "
"chapter about <link linkend=\"plugins\">plugins</link> for a description of "
"the various plugins."
msgstr ""
"Crida a la funció de <emphasis>configuració</emphasis> d'un connector, amb "
"una llista opcional de paràmetres. Si no s'indica cap llista de paràmetres, "
"s'utilitzaran els paràmetres de la crida anterior o amb els paràmetres "
"predeterminats. Normalment, es mostrarà un diàleg de configuració, depenent "
"del connector. Consulteu el capítol sobre els <link linkend=\"plugins"
"\">connectors</link> per a obtenir una descripció dels diferents connectors."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_prev;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_prev;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3300
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Previous</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips back to the previous label or start "
"of the selection. If the playback is not running, this does the same as the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Anterior</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. Si la "
"reproducció s'està executant, es passarà de nou a l'etiqueta anterior o al "
"començament de la selecció. Si la reproducció no s'està executant, aquesta "
"farà el mateix que l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</"
"command>()."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_next\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_next\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;q"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;q"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_quit;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_quit;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes the current main window, including all sub-windows. In SDI mode this "
"is the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Tanca la finestra principal, incloses totes les subfinestres secundàries. En "
"el mode SDI, això és el mateix que l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_close;</"
"command>()."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3338
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;r"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;r"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3341
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_redo;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_redo;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Redo</guibutton> toolbar button and repeats "
"one operation that has been reverted with <command>&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</"
"command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Refés</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i "
"repeteix una operació que s'ha revertit amb <command>&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</"
"command>()."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3352 index.docbook:3368 index.docbook:3826
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3358
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <command>&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>(), but re-does as many "
"operations as possible."
msgstr ""
"Similar a <command>&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>(), però tornarà a fer tantes "
"operacions com sigui possible."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3374
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some message boxes offer the possibility to prevent them from appearing "
"again (<quote>do not ask again</quote>). This command makes all of them "
"appear again."
msgstr ""
"Alguns quadres de missatge ofereixen la possibilitat d'evitar que tornin a "
"aparèixer («No ho tornis a preguntar»). Aquesta ordre farà que tots tornin a "
"aparèixer."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resets all toolbar settings, like location, icon size and text location back "
"to defaults."
msgstr ""
"Restaura totes les opcions de la barra d'eines, com ara la ubicació, la mida "
"de la icona i la ubicació del text a la configuració predeterminada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_revert;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_revert;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3399
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_revert;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_revert;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reverts the currently loaded file back to the last saved state, discarding "
"all changes that are not saved."
msgstr ""
"Reverteix el fitxer carregat a l'últim estat desat, descartant tots els "
"canvis que no s'hagin desat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3408
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3410
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Rewind</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips backward by 1/10 of the visible "
"range. If the playback is not running, this does the same as the command "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Rebobina</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. Si la "
"reproducció s'està executant, això saltarà cap enrere per 1/10 de l'interval "
"visible. Si la reproducció no s'està executant, aquesta farà el mateix que "
"l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_left\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_forward"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_forward;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_left\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_forward"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_forward;</command>()</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3428
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;s"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;s"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3431
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_save;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_save;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> toolbar button. Saves the "
"current file if it has modifications. If the file does not already have a "
"name (&eg; a file that has just been created and does not yet have a file "
"name), this command does the same as <command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>()."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Desa</guibutton> de la barra d'eines. Desa el "
"fitxer actual si conté modificacions. Si el fitxer encara no té un nom "
"(&pex;, un fitxer que s'acaba de crear i que encara no té un nom de fitxer), "
"aquesta ordre farà el mateix que <command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</command>()."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3450
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>([<replaceable>filename</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>([<replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the currently opened file under a given file name. If no file name is "
"given as parameter, a dialog will be shown to select the directory and to "
"enter a file name."
msgstr ""
"Desa el fitxer obert sota un nom de fitxer indicat. Si no s'indica cap nom "
"de fitxer com a paràmetre, es mostrarà un diàleg per a seleccionar el "
"directori i per a introduir un nom de fitxer."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3461
#, no-c-format
msgid "file name for saving (optional)"
msgstr "nom del fitxer per a desar (opcional)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command does the same as <command>&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>(), but "
"saves only the currently selected range and the activated tracks instead of "
"the whole file."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta ordre fa el mateix que <command>&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>(), però "
"només desarà l'interval seleccionat i les pistes activades en comptes de tot "
"el fitxer."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3483
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;</"
"command>(<replaceable>mode</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;</"
"command>(<replaceable>mode</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a &GUI; mode, which can be either SDI, MDI or Tab mode. Please be "
"aware that this change will immediately take effect!"
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un mode d'&IGU;, el qual pot ser el mode SDI, MDI o Tab "
"(Pestanyes). Tingueu en compte que aquest canvi tindrà efecte immediat!"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"name of the mode, must be either <quote>SDI</quote>, <quote>MDI</quote> or "
"<quote>TAB</quote>."
msgstr "nom del mode, haurà de ser «SDI», «MDI» o «Tab» (Pestanyes)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3502
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3504 index.docbook:3521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark all tracks <quote>enabled</quote>. This is the same as calling the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>() for "
"all existing tracks."
msgstr ""
"Marca totes les pistes «habilitades». Això és el mateix que cridar a l'ordre "
"<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>() per a totes "
"les pistes existents."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3519
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_invert;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_invert;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invert the <quote>enabled</quote> state of all tracks. This is the same as "
"calling the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>() "
"for all existing tracks."
msgstr ""
"Inverteix l'estat «habilitada» de totes les pistes. Això és el mateix que "
"cridar a l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>() per "
"a totes les pistes existents."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3531
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3537
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark all tracks <quote>disabled</quote>. This is the same as calling the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>() for all existing "
"tracks."
msgstr ""
"Marca totes les pistes «inhabilitades». Això és el mateix que cridar a "
"l'ordre <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>() per a totes les "
"pistes existents."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3548
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3554
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disables a single track, so that it does not get affected by most operations."
msgstr ""
"Inhabilita una sola pista, de manera que no es vegi afectada per la majoria "
"de les operacions."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3564 index.docbook:3578 index.docbook:3593
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the track, starting with zero"
msgstr "índex de la pista, començant pel zero"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3572
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables a single track, so that it gets affected by all operations."
msgstr ""
"Habilita una única pista, de manera que es vegi afectada per totes les "
"operacions."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</"
"command>(<replaceable>índex</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables a track if it is currently disabled, or disables it if it is "
"currently enabled."
msgstr ""
"Habilita una pista si està inhabilitada o la inhabilita si està habilitada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3598
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the range of the whole signal, from the first to the last sample."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona l'interval de tot el senyal, des de la primera fins a l'última "
"mostra."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3609
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples that starts right after the current selection, "
"using the same length as the current selection. The selection is "
"automatically clipped to the end of the signal. For example: if you have "
"selected samples 1000 ... 1019, then the result will be a selection from "
"sample 1020 ... 1039."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un interval de mostres que començarà just després de la selecció "
"actual, utilitzant la mateixa longitud que la selecció actual. La selecció "
"es retallarà automàticament fins al final del senyal. Per exemple: si heu "
"seleccionat les mostres 1000 fins a la 1019, el resultat serà una selecció "
"des de la mostra 1020 fins a la 1039."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3622
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3628
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples between the next two labels after the current "
"selection. If nothing is selected, it selects from the start of the signal "
"up to the first label. Otherwise the left border of the new selection will "
"be the position of first label after the selection (or the last label if "
"there are no more labels right from the selection), and the right border of "
"the new selection will be the first label after the left border of the new "
"selection (or the end of the signal if there is none). This command returns "
"an error when there are no labels at all."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un interval de mostres entre les dues etiquetes següents després "
"de la selecció actual. Si no se selecciona res, això seleccionarà des del "
"començament del senyal fins a la primera etiqueta. En cas contrari, la vora "
"esquerra de la selecció nova serà la posició de la primera etiqueta després "
"de la selecció (o l'última etiqueta si no hi ha més etiquetes a la dreta de "
"la selecció), i la vora dreta de la selecció nova serà la primera etiqueta "
"després de la vora esquerra de la selecció nova (o el final del senyal si no "
"n'hi ha cap). Aquesta ordre retornarà un error quan no hi hagi cap etiqueta."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resets the selection to zero length."
msgstr "Restaura la selecció a la longitud zero."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples that starts left from the current selection, "
"using the same length as the current selection. The selection is "
"automatically clipped to the start of the signal. For example: if you have "
"selected samples 1000 ... 1019, then the result will be a selection from "
"sample 980 ... 999."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un interval de mostres que començarà a l'esquerra de la selecció "
"actual, utilitzant la mateixa longitud que la selecció actual. La selecció "
"es retallarà automàticament fins al començament del senyal. Per exemple: si "
"heu seleccionat les mostres 1000 fins a la 1019, el resultat serà una "
"selecció des de la mostra 980 fins a la 999."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples between the previous two labels before the "
"current selection. If nothing is selected, it selects from the start of the "
"signal up to the first label. Otherwise the right border of the new "
"selection will be the position of first label before the selection (or the "
"first label if there are no more labels left from the selection), and the "
"left border of the new selection will be the first label before the right "
"border of the new selection (or the start of the signal if there is none). "
"This command returns an error when there are no labels at all."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un interval de mostres entre les dues etiquetes anteriors abans "
"de la selecció actual. Si no se selecciona res, això seleccionarà des del "
"començament del senyal fins a la primera etiqueta. En cas contrari, la vora "
"dreta de la selecció nova serà la posició de la primera etiqueta abans de la "
"selecció (o la primera etiqueta si no hi ha més etiquetes a la selecció), i "
"la vora esquerra de la selecció nova serà la primera etiqueta abans de la "
"vora dreta de la selecció nova (o el començament del senyal si no n'hi ha "
"cap). Aquesta ordre retornarà un error quan no hi hagi cap etiqueta."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3703
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the start of the selection to the start of the signal, the end of the "
"current selection stays unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Estableix el començament de la selecció al començament del senyal, el final "
"de la selecció actual romandrà sense canvis."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3713
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoright;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the end of the selection to the end of the signal, the start of the "
"current selection stays unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Estableix el final de la selecció al final del senyal, el començament de la "
"selecció actual romandrà sense canvis."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3729
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3735
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectvisible;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectvisible;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectvisible;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectvisible;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the range of samples that is visible in the current window."
msgstr "Selecciona l'interval de mostres que és visible a la finestra actual."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3746
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_start;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_start;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3748
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_start;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback start from the beginning of the selection or continue if it is "
"currently paused."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Inicia</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i permet "
"iniciar la reproducció des del començament de la selecció o continua si està "
"en pausa."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3757
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_stop;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_stop;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3763
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_stop;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_stop;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3765
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_stop;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_stop;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback stop if it is currently running."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Atura</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i permet "
"que la reproducció s'aturi si s'està executant."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_start;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_sync;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_sync;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3781
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_sync;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_sync;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3782
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Waits until all commands which have been started asynchronously have "
"finished. If nothing is currently queued for delayed execution this command "
"has no effect."
msgstr ""
"Espera fins que finalitzin totes les ordres iniciades de forma asíncrona. Si "
"no hi ha res en curs a la cua per a una execució retardada, aquesta ordre no "
"tindrà cap efecte."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3790
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_delayed;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3797
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;u"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;u"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_undo;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_undo;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3802
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Undo</guibutton> toolbar button and reverts "
"the last operation."
msgstr ""
"Correspon al botó <guibutton>Desfés</guibutton> de la barra d'eines i "
"reverteix l'última operació."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3816
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_undo_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_undo_all;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo_all;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo_all;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>(), but reverts "
"as many operations as possible."
msgstr ""
"Similar a <command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>(), però "
"reverteix la quantitat més gran possible d'operacions."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3832
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;v"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;v"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3835
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolls the current view to the <emphasis>end</emphasis> of the signal."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça la vista actual fins al <emphasis>final</emphasis> del senyal."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3842
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3848
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls the current view by 1/10 of the currently visible range towards the "
"start of the signal. If the start of the signal is reached the visible area "
"starts at offset zero."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça la vista actual per 1/10 de l'interval visible cap al començament "
"del senyal. Si s'abasta el començament del senyal, l'àrea visible començarà "
"al zero."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3859
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3865
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls the current view towards the end of the signal by the currently "
"visible range."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça la vista actual cap al final del senyal per a l'interval visible."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3875
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3881
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls right and tries to show the next label centered in the view. If "
"there was no label right from the current position, it will scroll to the "
"end of the signal."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça cap a la dreta i intenta mostrar l'etiqueta següent centrada a la "
"vista. Si no hi ha cap etiqueta a la dreta des de la posició actual, es "
"desplaçarà fins al final del senyal."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3892
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3898
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls the current view towards the start of the signal by the currently "
"visible range."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça la vista actual cap al començament del senyal per a l'interval "
"visible."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3908
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls left and tries to show the previous label centered in the view. If "
"there was no label left from the current position, it will scroll to the "
"start of the signal."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça cap a l'esquerra i intenta mostrar l'anterior etiqueta centrada a "
"la vista. Si no hi ha cap etiqueta a l'esquerra des de la posició actual, es "
"desplaçarà fins al començament del senyal."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3925
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3931
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_right;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls the current view by 1/10 of the currently visible range towards the "
"end of the signal. If the end of the signal is reached the visible area ends "
"at the end of the signal."
msgstr ""
"Desplaça la vista actual per 1/10 de l'interval visible cap al final del "
"senyal. Si s'abasta el final del senyal, l'àrea visible finalitzarà al final "
"del senyal."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3948
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_start;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolls the current view to the start of the signal."
msgstr "Desplaça la vista actual cap al començament del senyal."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3955
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_end;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3961
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_all;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_all;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_all;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjusts the zoom factor so that the complete signal is visible in the "
"current view."
msgstr ""
"Ajusta el factor d'apropament perquè sigui visible tot el senyal a la vista "
"actual."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3972
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;</"
"command>([<replaceable>position</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;</"
"command>([<replaceable>posició</replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the zoom factor (in samples per pixel) by 30%, so that more details "
"get visible. If a <replaceable>position</replaceable> is given, it tries to "
"show that position centered in the current view, otherwise the center of the "
"view before the zoom change is used for centering. The minimum zoom factor "
"is limited to a minimum of five samples per width of the view."
msgstr ""
"Redueix el factor d'apropament (en mostres per píxel) en un 30%, de manera "
"que es puguin veure més detalls. Si s'indica una <replaceable>posició</"
"replaceable>, l'intentarà mostrar centrada a la vista actual, en cas "
"contrari, s'utilitzarà el centre de la vista abans del canvi d'apropament. "
"El factor d'apropament estarà limitat a un mínim de cinc mostres per amplada "
"de la vista."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3987 index.docbook:4024
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>position</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>posició</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3988
#, no-c-format
msgid "a zero based position in samples to center the view (optional)"
msgstr ""
"una posició basada en mostres i amb origen zero per a centrar la vista "
"(opcional)"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3998
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_normal;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_normal;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_normal;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_normal;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the zoom factor to one pixel per sample (factor 1.0) and tries to keep "
"the previous center of the view."
msgstr ""
"Estableix el factor d'apropament en un píxel per mostra (factor 1,0) i "
"intentarà mantenir el centre anterior de la vista."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4009
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;"
"([<replaceable>position</replaceable>])</command>"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_out;([<replaceable>posició</"
"replaceable>])</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the zoom factor (in samples per pixel) by 30%, so that less "
"details get visible. If a <replaceable>position</replaceable> is given, it "
"tries to show that position centered in the current view, otherwise the "
"center of the view before the zoom change is used for centering. The maximum "
"zoom factor is limited to the number of samples of the complete signal and "
"the width of the view."
msgstr ""
"Augmenta el factor d'apropament (en mostres per píxel) en un 30%, de manera "
"que es puguin veure menys detalls. Si s'indica una <replaceable>posició</"
"replaceable>, l'intentarà mostrar centrada a la vista actual, en cas "
"contrari, s'utilitzarà el centre de la vista abans del canvi d'apropament. "
"El factor d'apropament estarà limitat al nombre de mostres de tot el senyal "
"i l'amplada de la vista."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4025
#, no-c-format
msgid "a zero based position is samples to center the view (optional)"
msgstr ""
"una posició basada en mostres i amb origen zero per a centrar la vista "
"(opcional)"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:4029
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_in;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4035
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_selection;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_selection;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_selection;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_selection;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4038
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjusts the view (zoom factor and start of visible area) so that it matches "
"the current selection. This command does nothing if the selection is empty."
msgstr ""
"Ajusta la vista (factor d'apropament i el començament de l'àrea visible) de "
"manera que coincideixi amb la selecció actual. Aquesta ordre no farà res si "
"la selecció està buida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4047
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;w"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;w"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4050
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_activate;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_activate;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_activate;</"
"command>(<replaceable>title</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_activate;</"
"command>(<replaceable>títol</replaceable>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activates a sub-window, identified by its window <replaceable>title</"
"replaceable>. If the sub-window is minimized it will be restored. Only "
"available if in MDI and Tab mode. This command is internally used by the "
"<guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Activa una subfinestra, identificada pel seu <replaceable>títol</"
"replaceable> de finestra. Si es minimitza la subfinestra, es restaurarà. "
"Només disponible si està en el mode MDI i Pestanyes. Aquesta ordre és "
"utilitzada internament pel menú <guisubmenu>Finestra</guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4061
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>title</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>títol</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4062
#, no-c-format
msgid "the title of the sub-window that should be activated"
msgstr "el títol de la subfinestra que s'hauria d'activar"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4067
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_cascade;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_cascade;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_cascade;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_cascade;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cascades all sub-windows when in MDI mode. All sub-windows that are "
"currently minimized stay minimized, they will not be restored."
msgstr ""
"Mostra en cascada totes les subfinestres quan es troba en el mode MDI. Totes "
"les subfinestres minimitzades romandran minimitzades, no es restauraran."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4078
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable>, <replaceable>x</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>y</replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_click;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable>, <replaceable>x</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>y</replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a mouse click event to window, identified by its <replaceable>class</"
"replaceable> name. The event will only be sent to the first window that has "
"the given class name, therefore you should make sure that you have only one "
"instance of the given window when this command gets executed."
msgstr ""
"Envia un esdeveniment de clic del ratolí a la finestra, identificada pel seu "
"nom de <replaceable>classe</replaceable>. L'esdeveniment només s'enviarà a "
"la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la classe indicada, per tant, "
"haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una instància de la finestra indicada "
"quan s'executi aquesta ordre."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4095 index.docbook:4119 index.docbook:4153 index.docbook:4204
#: index.docbook:4232 index.docbook:4257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>class</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>classe</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4096 index.docbook:4120 index.docbook:4154 index.docbook:4205
#: index.docbook:4233 index.docbook:4258
#, no-c-format
msgid "name of the window class"
msgstr "nom de la classe de la finestra"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4097 index.docbook:4155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>x</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>x</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4098 index.docbook:4156
#, no-c-format
msgid "x position, relative to the left border of the window (in pixels)"
msgstr "posició X, relativa a la vora esquerra de la finestra (en píxels)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4099 index.docbook:4157
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>y</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>y</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4100 index.docbook:4158
#, no-c-format
msgid "y position, relative to the top border of the window (in pixels)"
msgstr "posició Y, relativa a la vora superior de la finestra (en píxels)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4105
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_close;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes a window, identified by its <replaceable>class</replaceable> name. "
"Only the first window that has the given class name will be closed, "
"therefore you should make sure that you have only one instance of the given "
"window when this command gets executed."
msgstr ""
"Tanca una finestra, identificada pel seu nom de <replaceable>classe</"
"replaceable>. Només es tancarà la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la "
"classe indicada, per tant, haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una "
"instància de la finestra indicada quan s'executi aquesta ordre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4125
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_minimize;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_minimize;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4127
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_minimize;</command>"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_minimize;</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Minimizes the currently active sub-window when in MDI mode or the current "
"toplevel window when in SDI or Tab mode."
msgstr ""
"Minimitza la subfinestra activa quan està en el mode MDI o la finestra de "
"nivell superior quan es troba en el mode SDI o Pestanyes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4136
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_mousemove;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_mousemove;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable>, <replaceable>x</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>y</replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable>, <replaceable>x</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>y</replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a mouse move event to window, identified by its <replaceable>class</"
"replaceable> name. The event will only be sent to the first window that has "
"the given class name, therefore you should make sure that you have only one "
"instance of the given window when this command gets executed."
msgstr ""
"Envia un esdeveniment de moviment del ratolí a la finestra, identificat pel "
"seu nom de <replaceable>classe</replaceable>. L'esdeveniment només s'enviarà "
"a la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la classe indicada, per tant, "
"haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una instància de la finestra indicada "
"quan s'executi aquesta ordre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4163
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_next_sub;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_next_sub;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_next_sub;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_next_sub;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activates the <emphasis>next</emphasis> sub-window when in MDI or Tab mode. "
"If the next sub-window is minimized it will be restored."
msgstr ""
"Activa la <emphasis>següent</emphasis> subfinestra quan es troba en el mode "
"MDI o Pestanyes. Si subfinestra següent està minimitzada, es restaurarà."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4174
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_prev_sub;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_prev_sub;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_prev_sub;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_prev_sub;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activates the <emphasis>previous</emphasis> sub-window when in MDI or Tab "
"mode. If the previous sub-window is minimized it will be restored."
msgstr ""
"Activa la subfinestra <emphasis>anterior</emphasis> quan es troba en el mode "
"MDI o Tab. Si la subfinestra anterior està minimitzada, es restaurarà."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4185
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable>, <replaceable>width</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>height</replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_resize;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable>, <replaceable>amplada</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>alçada</replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes the size of a window, identified by its <replaceable>class</"
"replaceable> name to a new <replaceable>width</replaceable> and "
"<replaceable>height</replaceable>. The change will only be applied to the "
"first window that has the given class name, therefore you should make sure "
"that you have only one instance of the given window when this command gets "
"executed."
msgstr ""
"Canvia la mida d'una finestra, identificada pel seu nom de "
"<replaceable>classe</replaceable> a una amplada i alçada nova. El canvi "
"només s'aplicarà a la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la classe "
"indicada, per tant, haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una instància de "
"la finestra indicada quan s'executi aquesta ordre."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>width</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>amplada</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4207
#, no-c-format
msgid "new width of the window (in pixels)"
msgstr "l'amplada nova de la finestra (en píxels)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>height</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>alçada</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4209
#, no-c-format
msgid "new height of the window (in pixels)"
msgstr "l'alçada nova de la finestra (en píxels)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4214
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable>, <replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_screenshot;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable>, <replaceable>nom_de_fitxer</"
"replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Takes a screenshot of a window, identified by its <replaceable>class</"
"replaceable> and saves it to a file. The screenshot will be taken from the "
"first window that has the given class name, therefore you should make sure "
"that you have only one instance of the given window when this command gets "
"executed. Currently the format of the file is hardcoded and has to be "
"<literal>*.png</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Pren una captura de pantalla d'una finestra, identificada per la seva "
"<replaceable>classe</replaceable> i la desa en un fitxer. La captura de "
"pantalla serà presa de la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la classe "
"indicada, per tant, haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una instància de "
"la finestra indicada quan s'executi aquesta ordre. Actualment, el format del "
"fitxer és fix i haurà de ser <literal>*.png</literal>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"name of the file to save the screenshot, must have the extension <literal>*."
"png</literal>"
msgstr ""
"nom del fitxer per a desar la captura de pantalla, haurà de tenir l'extensió "
"<literal>*.png</literal>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4241
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;</"
"command>( <replaceable>class</replaceable>, <replaceable>key code</"
"replaceable> )"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_window_sendkey;</"
"command>( <replaceable>classe</replaceable>, <replaceable>codi_clau</"
"replaceable> )"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a key press and release event to a window, identified by its "
"<replaceable>class</replaceable> name. The key will only be sent to the "
"first window that has the given class name, therefore you should make sure "
"that you have only one instance of the given window when this command gets "
"executed."
msgstr ""
"Envia un esdeveniment de pulsació i alliberament de tecla a la finestra, "
"identificada pel seu nom de <replaceable>classe</replaceable>. La tecla "
"només s'enviarà a la primera finestra que tingui el nom de la classe "
"indicada, per tant, haureu d'assegurar-vos que només teniu una instància de "
"la finestra indicada quan s'executi aquesta ordre."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4259
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>key code</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>codi_clau</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:4260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the key code that should be sent, using the same syntax as used for setting "
"up menus"
msgstr ""
"el codi clau que s'ha d'enviar, utilitzant la mateixa sintaxi que s'utilitza "
"per a configurar els menús"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Description of the parameter <link linkend=\"cmd_menu_param_hotkey"
"\"><parameter>hotkey</parameter></link> of the <command>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</"
"command>() command."
msgstr ""
"La descripció del paràmetre <link linkend=\"cmd_menu_param_hotkey"
"\"><parameter>drecera de teclat</parameter></link> de l'ordre <command>&no-"
"i18n-cmd_menu;</command>()."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4273
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tiles all sub-windows when in MDI mode, using some scheme of &plasma;. All "
"sub-windows that are currently minimized stay minimized, they will not be "
"restored."
msgstr ""
"Mostra en mosaic totes les subfinestres quan es troba en el mode MDI, "
"utilitzant algun esquema del &plasma;. Totes les subfinestres minimitzades "
"romandran minimitzades, no es restauraran."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4285
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile_vertical;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile_vertical;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile_vertical;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_window_tile_vertical;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tiles all sub-windows vertically when in MDI mode. All windows that are "
"currently minimized stay minimized, they will not be restored."
msgstr ""
"Mostra en mosaic vertical totes les subfinestres quan es troba en el mode "
"MDI. Totes les finestres minimitzades romandran minimitzades, no es "
"restauraran."

